{"data":[{"id":559470347,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559470347","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545729731,"updated_time":1545736237,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e如果题主真的证明出哥德巴赫猜想，那将在数学史上留下色彩浓厚的一笔。（前提是得到专家们的认可)\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e保送清北是不大可能了，直接会被大佬机构预定，会满足你合理的条件\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e…………………………………………………………………………\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e作为某二本院校（拉低知乎平均学历）应用数学专业狗，从理论上来说，这不大可能，但从个人情感来说，我希望这是真的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e等明年1月1号\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559456561,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"d19d4457a7e3dba41a0a0cdbdeed4544","url_token":"san-yue-de-jiu","name":"鱼沉","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-91c6e74032aab55a7e2609634b8956b8_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-91c6e74032aab55a7e2609634b8956b8_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/d19d4457a7e3dba41a0a0cdbdeed4544","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559456561","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545728444,"updated_time":1545728444,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e都这样了还上什么大学啊\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559268670,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"8b1808cc12a9bd1b6a894a779ab497ef","url_token":"wang-zhi-ping-19-91","name":"岚山扇贝","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/eaf77fbdfd2e06bcf8cdb5cba4053337_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/eaf77fbdfd2e06bcf8cdb5cba4053337_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/8b1808cc12a9bd1b6a894a779ab497ef","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559268670","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545712081,"updated_time":1545712081,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e期待脸\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":557840470,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"5d036f5b9dccbb2dac642cb9a3292bb5","url_token":"luo-mo-34-80","name":"罗莫","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2f1c2342ee81ea2d8eae0cfc6db6569e_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2f1c2342ee81ea2d8eae0cfc6db6569e_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/5d036f5b9dccbb2dac642cb9a3292bb5","user_type":"people","headline":"心开者，幼冲而即悟；意闭者，皓首而难精。","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/557840470","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545535159,"updated_time":1545535159,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e支持你的＂如果＂，不认同你的＂那么＂。你的＂如果＂有实现的可能，当年的伽罗华就和你一般大，但解决了当时一流的数学问题，并开创了现代数学，英雄不问出处，包括年龄。至于能不能用初等的方法解决，回答是可以的，虽不简单，有时会比高等的更难，但必有希望，一切高等都是通过初等构造出来的，别听那些给你泼冷水的人。但你的＂那么＂，的确动机没摆正，探索数学真理是为了解决更深刻的数学真理，至于如何被认可，是顺带收获，包括一流数学杂志愿发表你的论文。你的东西被追随是别人的事，你可以不断探索出新知是你的最大成功，其他都是次要的。更不要本末倒置去追求真理。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560484943,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"abc716ddf6eee50b69c4da8e90f8d0d6","url_token":"yu-sheng-de-di-yi-tian","name":"小四十一呀","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-f3cb291b106cbbf2a79ba136dc7d1ef2_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-f3cb291b106cbbf2a79ba136dc7d1ef2_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/abc716ddf6eee50b69c4da8e90f8d0d6","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560484943","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545841743,"updated_time":1545979590,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e这个问题争执得我的头都痛了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我觉得这并没有有些人说的那么夸张的程度，他错了，告诉他错了就行了，我并没有觉得他侮辱了科学家侮辱了数学。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果他真的是为了装逼提出了这个问题，那么现在这么多人正儿八经的把这事提出来争执，那不就达到他的目的了？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e每个人的想法不一样，我理解不了为什么你们选择这样去嘲讽他，但是看了那么多评论大概也有种模糊的概念了。在你们看来他真的那么不可理喻的话，直接忽视他难道不更好吗？如果直接不理会他他不过是个跳梁小丑根本不会有人在意他，正是因为你们这么多人正儿八经的把这事拎出来说了去争执了，才显得他说他证明出了哥德巴赫猜想这件事真的成了一件事了【不知道能不能懂我的意思orz】\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们可以选择去嘲讽他，但是在我自己看来，可以但没必要。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e--------------下面是原答案---------------\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e看了一些答案，有些人在嘲讽提问者，我就emmmm，不管提问者是不是年轻气盛心高气傲还是中二病初生牛犊不怕虎，至少在很多人每天很丧的生活，每天在床上躺尸【我自己╭(°A°`)╮】的情况下，他愿意在这上面去花功夫去研究，不管结果怎么样，我觉得这是很棒的事啊。为什么偏要去嘲讽他呢？对一个高中生抱有善意很难吗？？？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不管最后他有没有证明出来，希望他能被大家温柔以待(ง •̀_•́)ง\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560186813,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"43790bc7166f65aeb49ca103f83b6855","url_token":"he-nan-88","name":"何南","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a47b0a484712d4ec368721d8660e9809_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a47b0a484712d4ec368721d8660e9809_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/43790bc7166f65aeb49ca103f83b6855","user_type":"people","headline":"云雾苍茫各一天，可怜西北起烽烟\n东来暴客西来盗，还有胡儿在眼前","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560186813","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545816388,"updated_time":1545816388,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":18,"content":"\u003cp\u003e高斯17岁尺规作正十七边形，牛顿22岁发明微积分，爱因斯坦26岁发表狭义相对论，我生的晚，这三个历史时刻都没有遇到，难道一月一日要见到人类科学史第四个伟大时刻？我好期待！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562592435,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"ab2b651c629eb54e3ddccea9caef817e","url_token":"mu-shi-han-37","name":"暮湿寒","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3aca97630d87974e8320db41304aaaef_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3aca97630d87974e8320db41304aaaef_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/ab2b651c629eb54e3ddccea9caef817e","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562592435","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546105255,"updated_time":1546105286,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e所有高赞答案都没有正面回答问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e题主问的是高中生证明哥德巴赫猜想能否保送清北，什么题主证明不出来，清北不是最好的，什么不如当教授等等都不是这个问题的回答，所有高赞答案全都审题不清。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我来正面回答这个问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先，我的回答是，不能。至少是不能直接的保送，不管哥德巴赫猜想多难证，你看起来有多牛。这是因为，直接保送这不合“规矩”。据我所知，国家规定的可能有保送资格有省级优秀学生，竞赛集训队，运动员，外国语，烈士子女等。显然，证明哥德巴赫猜想不属于其中任何一类，所以答案是不能保送。如果让你在规矩之外保送，保送制度就乱了套了，比如我救人能不能保送？人命难道没个破猜想重要？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过，规矩是死的，人是活的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你的实力得到了国家的认可，国家认为有必要争取你这个人才，不让你外流，而你只要上清北。国家可以在规矩限定之内给你最大的上清北的可能。比如你数学好，那就让你参加数学竞赛，大不了提前给你泄题，组织改卷老师认你的字迹，让你轻轻松松进集训队，这样就符合规矩了。或者给你个运动员证明保送，再给你个运动员训练因公受伤的证明堵别人的口也可以符合规矩等等。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e总之，规矩不能破，在规矩之内，可以全力“操作”。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过，不过哥德巴赫猜想再难证，也算是理论数学范畴，这种人国家应该还没有举国争取的欲望，要是应用物理或者工程方向的国家应该会有兴趣得多。当然，清北数学系教授可能会叹服于你的水平，但是单凭教授们也操作不了太多，顶多自主招生你当哑巴交白卷也强行给你降到一本线，你还是得高考。何况现在自招那么透明，稍微被人举报教授就不用做了，我猜教授们顶多加你个好友和你交流交流，在升学方面帮不了你太多。不过有了这些资源，你不读大学混理论数学圈也没问题，大不了破格录取你当讲师，当讲师的规矩一个学校就能操作。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以，答案是不行。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其余的看看高赞答案，清北不是唯一出路，前提是真有人能证明。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560636087,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b22440dbdfda23b1eebaabb2f57e0fec","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560636087","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545875738,"updated_time":1545875738,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我证明出了哥猜，说到哥猜——\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e明年年初，中美合拍的西游记即将正式开机，我将继续扮演美猴王孙悟空，我会用美猴王艺术形象努力创造一个正能量的形象，文体两开花，弘扬中华文化，希望大家多多关注。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560481979,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"19ec14de345f322b6265c8f3a955863c","url_token":"qi-zhi-fa-43","name":"弃治发","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/19ec14de345f322b6265c8f3a955863c","user_type":"people","headline":"哈哈哈","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560481979","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545841453,"updated_time":1545841453,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不管是不是真的证明出来了，我感觉他也已经很优秀了，为什么评论冷嘲热讽的，鼓励鼓励不好吗？又不是做了什么坏事，还扯什么非蠢即坏，柠檬精吧。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560178460,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"e3aff81480910a369b6a47316119401d","url_token":"xin-xuan-38-82","name":"xin xuan","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/e3aff81480910a369b6a47316119401d","user_type":"people","headline":"专业打字,","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560178460","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545815676,"updated_time":1545895814,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e下面一大堆人连哥德巴赫猜想,reimann zeta函数都不知道，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e就开始讽刺、嘲笑题主，好像他已经知道了证明过程并且推翻了一样。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e让我想起哥白尼被迫害，伽利略被嘲笑时的无知众人，既然啥都不懂，麻烦别急着下结论，OK？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那样会显得你们很无知。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e还有重庆公交坠江，女司机的遭遇。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然我也不懂，但是我会保留意见。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e不过虽然我也不太相信证明是真的，但是当时不也很多人不相信哥白尼吗？\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e如果有大佬表态说他的证明有误，马上删帖。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e没有的话，我等还是闭嘴吧。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562690806,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"99d7dc0a7ebabad7336fe0f72320d158","url_token":"you-xue-yuki","name":"又雪YUKI","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-38324fc56a86bf825828cf076c7a739c_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-38324fc56a86bf825828cf076c7a739c_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/99d7dc0a7ebabad7336fe0f72320d158","user_type":"people","headline":"游走在世界边缘的纸片人","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562690806","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546135770,"updated_time":1546135770,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e到那么多人对他冷嘲热讽，我想，万一这孩子忍受不了世俗中的这些恶语，逐渐自闭，那他本来可以光明的未来，是不是也因此而毁灭了呢。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我亲眼看过老师用一句“这孩子很丑”让一个孩子崩溃退学，原本很活泼的孩子，再也不敢大声说话，不敢在大家玩的时候活跃参与，甚至上街都不敢抬起头走路。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e语言有的时候真的是利器，伤人无形。良言一句三冬暖，恶语伤人六月寒。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有的人还说那么倨傲的孩子就该挫一挫他的锐气，这是为他着想，将来走上社会才能怎样怎样之类云云。但是这是他引以为傲的东西，当我们都把他的骄傲踩在脚底下冷嘲热讽的时候，我们和那些站在制高点上去批判的人有什么区别。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e每个年龄段都该有每个年龄段该承受的，我老师和我们说过一段话，我觉得很在理——\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e青春年华的你们就该张扬活泼一些，这是你们这个年龄段特有的东西。别人说你们有个性，在这个年纪就是一种褒奖。我不主张什么要圆滑通达，你们这个年纪就是该有棱有角的。该圆滑通达的是像我这种年纪该有的，因为有责任要扛，有家庭需要供养，社会需要什么样的人，那就等你们走上社会以后再说，你们现在还是学生，那就不该承受学生以外需要承受的东西。所以你们放肆一些，说几句大话，只要不过分，就算听起来天方夜谭也值得我去表扬。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我的学生时代也很倨傲，仗着自己在语文上知道的略多，总是写二三文章批判这或那。我不过是有一种表现欲来证明自己和别人不同。幸好我的老师们并未嘲笑我，说我不知天高地厚，给我写什么北大录取我的段子来讥讽我。而是鼓励我继续创作，夸奖我好的地方，另外常常说一些名人故事或借用一些小说桥段来提醒我，恃才傲物不可取。我现在回过头想，那些老师们个个都博学，我的那些文章那些话实在太不知好歹，但是老师却愿意包容我给我鼓励和支持。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e想起来，若那时有知乎，我一时倨傲来知乎说，如果我已证明胡适《红楼梦考证》中作者是曹雪芹是错误的，能不能上北大，再来接受这来自四面八方的嘲笑和讽刺，大约我早已不是现在的样子。而当年，我也找了诸多资料立证胡适的作者立论是错误的，并在老师办公室大发狂言。幸好各位老师们并没有嘲笑我，反而给我指出我论证中的错误并提供给我更多的资料，让我去探索更多的未知。现在想想，他们真是很包容很温柔的人啊。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果对方是个熊孩子，那我们该批判的首先也该是教育他的人，而后才是他。但是这个孩子只不过心中有不平之气，想要证明自己与众不同。这孩子能否证明哥猜暂且不说，但是数学他有兴趣并引以为傲，或许我们该去给他正确的引导，而不是肆意取笑，冷嘲热讽。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e现在网络上，都太苛刻了。我只一句话：\u003cb\u003e愿那孩子不被语言暴力伤害，能够以一种个性的姿态，去度过他本该精彩的学生时代。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562549034,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"9a48b9c9abf6749079641076faadc8e6","url_token":"yan-dou-33-17","name":"烟斗","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/9a48b9c9abf6749079641076faadc8e6","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562549034","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546099242,"updated_time":1546099330,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e只正面回答问题：如果前提成立，结果是肯定的。也就是说肯定能够被清华北大数学系保送的。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562544571,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"d36d06b4c89e288a606bdff763040c4e","url_token":"a-tui-qwq","name":"echoey","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-21e307dbfc32f6239b40093040d37127_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-21e307dbfc32f6239b40093040d37127_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/d36d06b4c89e288a606bdff763040c4e","user_type":"people","headline":"人民艺术家","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562544571","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546098740,"updated_time":1546098740,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我为什么看到这个问题第一反应是题主的眼界好窄啊。。什么被保送啊都不是谁。。要是真证出来了就是整个国家的骄傲了。。那么千万学子考数学前就不用拜陈景润而是拜你了哇 \u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562477974,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"5a965aca13b6d685e303c4e8eb57c73d","url_token":"shen-sao-qi","name":"神骚七","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7043d16e140a1a3cf8ffcab16a9152ba_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7043d16e140a1a3cf8ffcab16a9152ba_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/5a965aca13b6d685e303c4e8eb57c73d","user_type":"people","headline":"不啦不啦不卡卡","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562477974","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546091860,"updated_time":1546091860,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e高中考北大清华很简单的，认真（全身心的投入）研究高考试卷两年到三年就差不多了，哥德巴赫猜想   \u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562424613,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"89e659a946bb05a3202d920d90e88372","url_token":"mei-yitian-huan-le","name":"每一天欢乐","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c8f159c4c2909499be1958c9f4ac737c_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c8f159c4c2909499be1958c9f4ac737c_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/89e659a946bb05a3202d920d90e88372","user_type":"people","headline":"愿十里坡永远阳光明媚。","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"http